Miss Universe Zozibini Tunzi has been announced as one of the guests who will be interviewed by Trevor Noah on The Daily Show on Tuesday. The beauty queen made South Africans proud when she walked away with the Miss Universe crown on Sunday 8 December, getting reactions on social media from the likes of Oprah and Trevor himself. Now, just over a week after her win, Zozi will be sitting down with the Trevor on the popular late-night show for a chat.  "Screaming!! I'm so excited for this. thank you @TrevorNoah @TheDailyShow looking forward to it," Zozibini tweeted. Source: Channel24  